note:
I am a pensioned-off Canadian visa officer. A visa officer is a Canadian Foreign Service Officer who decides on immigration and temporary visa applications.

I have lived in Canada, India, England, the Philippines and Austria. I have done temporary duties in Seattle, Detroit, London, Paris (Yes, that was the best one, except Tel Aviv.), Bonn, Bucharest, Moscow, Accra, Tel Aviv, Damascus, Abu Dhabi.
